TITLE: Implementing iOS Runtime Detection
DESCRIPTION: iOS-specific implementation of determineCurrentRuntime that uses Platform.osFamily to determine the runtime environment.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jetbrains/kotlin-multiplatform-dev-docs/blob/master/topics/multiplatform-run-tests.md#2025-04-23_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
import kotlin.experimental.ExperimentalNativeApi
import kotlin.native.Platform

@OptIn(ExperimentalNativeApi::class)
actual fun determineCurrentRuntime(): CurrentRuntime {
    val name = Platform.osFamily.name.lowercase()
    return CurrentRuntime(name, null)
}
```

